  <entry>
    <title>hexo</title>
    <url>/2024/09/07/hexo/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="参考文档"><a href="#参考文档" class="headerlink" title="参考文档"></a>参考文档</h2><p><a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/">https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/</a></p>
<h2 id="环境"><a href="#环境" class="headerlink" title="环境"></a>环境</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt;node -v</span><br><span class="line">v22.2.0</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&gt;npm -v</span><br><span class="line">10.7.0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="安装hexo-cli"><a href="#安装hexo-cli" class="headerlink" title="安装hexo-cli"></a>安装hexo-cli</h2><p><code>npm install -g hexo-cli</code></p>
<h2 id="fork-hexo-starter仓库"><a href="#fork-hexo-starter仓库" class="headerlink" title="fork hexo-starter仓库"></a>fork hexo-starter仓库</h2><p><code>git clone https://gitee.com/my919/hexo-starter.git</code></p>
<h2 id="安装theme-next主题"><a href="#安装theme-next主题" class="headerlink" title="安装theme-next主题"></a>安装theme-next主题</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd hexo-starter</span><br><span class="line">git branch dev</span><br><span class="line">git checkout dev</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-theme-next</span><br><span class="line">copy &quot;.\node_modules\hexo-theme-next\_config.yml&quot; &quot;.\_config.next.yml&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>修改<code>_config.yml</code>配置 </p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">theme: next</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>修改<code>_config.next.yml</code></p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># Schemes</span><br><span class="line"># scheme: Muse</span><br><span class="line">#scheme: Mist</span><br><span class="line">#scheme: Pisces</span><br><span class="line">scheme: Gemini</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="开启中文"><a href="#开启中文" class="headerlink" title="开启中文"></a>开启中文</h2><p><code>_config.yml</code>中开启 </p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">language: zh-CN</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="开启菜单"><a href="#开启菜单" class="headerlink" title="开启菜单"></a>开启菜单</h2><p><code>_config.next.yml</code> 的 <code>menu</code> 配置全部启用,执行以下命令创建菜单目录</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">menu:</span><br><span class="line">  home: / || fa fa-home</span><br><span class="line">  about: /about/ || fa fa-user</span><br><span class="line">  tags: /tags/ || fa fa-tags</span><br><span class="line">  categories: /categories/ || fa fa-th</span><br><span class="line">  archives: /archives/ || fa fa-archive</span><br><span class="line">  schedule: /schedule/ || fa fa-calendar</span><br><span class="line">  sitemap: /sitemap.xml || fa fa-sitemap</span><br><span class="line">  commonweal: /404/ || fa fa-heartbeat</span><br><span class="line">  study: /study/ || fa fa-school</span><br><span class="line">  math: /math/ || fa fa-calculator</span><br><span class="line">  art: /art/ || fa fa-palette</span><br><span class="line">  tools: /tools/ || fa fa-tools</span><br><span class="line">  books: /books/ || fa fa-book</span><br><span class="line">  blockchain: /blockchain/ || fa fa-chain</span><br><span class="line">  linux: /linux/ || fa fa-certificate</span><br><span class="line">  k8s: /k8s/ || fa fa-bus</span><br><span class="line">  pytorch: /pytorch/ || fa fa-paw</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>创建菜单目录</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo-starter&gt;hexo new page about</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Validating config</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Created: hexo-starter\source\about\index.md</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo-starter&gt;hexo new page tags</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Validating config</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Created: hexo-starter\source\tags\index.md</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo-starter&gt;hexo new page categories</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Validating config</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Created: hexo-starter\source\categories\index.md</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo-starter&gt;hexo new page schedule</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Validating config</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Created: hexo-starter\source\schedule\index.md</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo-starter&gt;hexo new page 404</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Validating config</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Created: hexo-starter\source\404\index.md</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo-starter&gt;hexo new page books</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Validating config</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Created: hexo-starter\source\books\index.md</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo-starter&gt;hexo new page study</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Validating config</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Created: hexo-starter\source\study\index.md</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo-starter&gt;hexo new page tools</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Validating config</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Created: hexo-starter\source\tools\index.md</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo-starter&gt;hexo new page math</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Validating config</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Created: hexo-starter\source\math\index.md</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo-starter&gt;hexo new page art</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Validating config</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Created: hexo-starter\source\art\index.md</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo-starter&gt;hexo new page blockchain</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Validating config</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Created: hexo-starter\source\blockchain\index.md</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo-starter&gt;hexo new page k8s</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Validating config</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Created: hexo-starter\source\k8s\index.md</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo-starter&gt;hexo new page linux</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Validating config</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Created: hexo-starter\source\linux\index.md</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo-starter&gt;hexo new page pytorch</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Validating config</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Created: hexo-starter\source\pytorch\index.md</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>复制语言文件</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">copy &quot;.\node_modules\hexo-theme-next\languages\zh-CN.yml&quot; &quot;.\zh-CN.yml&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>设置新建page的中文翻译, <strong>之后需要中文显示的，在<code>.\zh-CN.yml</code>中对于位置设置，然后再发布之前覆盖node_modules下的对应文件</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">menu:</span><br><span class="line">  home: 首页</span><br><span class="line">  archives: 归档</span><br><span class="line">  categories: 分类</span><br><span class="line">  tags: 标签</span><br><span class="line">  about: 关于</span><br><span class="line">  search: 搜索</span><br><span class="line">  schedule: 日程表</span><br><span class="line">  sitemap: 站点地图</span><br><span class="line">  commonweal: 公益 404</span><br><span class="line">  books: 书籍</span><br><span class="line">  study: 学习</span><br><span class="line">  tools: 工具</span><br><span class="line">  math: 数学</span><br><span class="line">  art: 艺术</span><br><span class="line">  blockchain: 区块链</span><br><span class="line">  k8s: 云原生</span><br><span class="line">  linux: Linux</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><code>_config.next.yml</code>中启用菜单</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">menu:</span><br><span class="line">  home: / || fa fa-home</span><br><span class="line">  about: /about/ || fa fa-user</span><br><span class="line">  tags: /tags/ || fa fa-tags</span><br><span class="line">  categories: /categories/ || fa fa-th</span><br><span class="line">  archives: /archives/ || fa fa-archive</span><br><span class="line">  schedule: /schedule/ || fa fa-calendar</span><br><span class="line">  sitemap: /sitemap.xml || fa fa-sitemap</span><br><span class="line">  commonweal: /404/ || fa fa-heartbeat</span><br><span class="line">  study: /study/ || fa fa-school</span><br><span class="line">  math: /math/ || fa fa-calculator</span><br><span class="line">  art: /art/ || fa fa-palette</span><br><span class="line">  tools: /tools/ || fa fa-tools</span><br><span class="line">  books: /books/ || fa fa-book</span><br><span class="line">  blockchain: /blockchain/ || fa fa-chain</span><br><span class="line">  linux: /linux/ || fa fa-certificate</span><br><span class="line">  k8s: /k8s/ || fa fa-bus</span><br><span class="line">  pytorch: /pytorch/ || fa fa-pytorch</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>将本地修改的语言翻译替换<code>node_modules\hexo-theme-next\languages\zh-CN.yml</code></p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">copy  &quot;.\zh-CN.yml&quot; &quot;.\node_modules\hexo-theme-next\languages\zh-CN.yml&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="设置github-pages"><a href="#设置github-pages" class="headerlink" title="设置github pages"></a>设置github pages</h2><ol>
<li>执行 <code>npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</code></li>
<li><code>_config.yml</code> 修改 <code>deploy</code> 节点如下：</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  - type: git</span><br><span class="line">    repo: </span><br><span class="line">      github: https://github.com/my0521/my0521.github.io.git   </span><br><span class="line">    branch: </span><br><span class="line">      github: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ol start="3">
<li>执行 <code>hexo clean &amp; hexo deploy</code></li>
</ol>
<h2 id="站内搜索"><a href="#站内搜索" class="headerlink" title="站内搜索"></a>站内搜索</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-generator-searchdb</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>启用配置 <code>_config.next.yml</code></p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">local_search:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="文章字数统计"><a href="#文章字数统计" class="headerlink" title="文章字数统计"></a>文章字数统计</h2><ol>
<li>安装依赖： <code>npm install hexo-word-counter</code></li>
<li><code>_config.next.yml</code>配置<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">symbols_count_time:</span><br><span class="line">  separated_meta: true</span><br><span class="line">  item_text_total: true</span><br><span class="line">  symbols: true</span><br><span class="line">  time: true</span><br><span class="line">  total_symbols: true</span><br><span class="line">  total_time: true</span><br><span class="line">  exclude_codeblock: false</span><br><span class="line">  wpm: 275</span><br><span class="line">  suffix: &quot;mins.&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
</ol>
<h2 id="设置github-banner"><a href="#设置github-banner" class="headerlink" title="设置github_banner"></a>设置github_banner</h2><p><code>_config.next.yml</code>配置</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">github_banner:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  permalink: https://github.com/my0521</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="开启社交链接"><a href="#开启社交链接" class="headerlink" title="开启社交链接"></a>开启社交链接</h2><p><code>_config.next.yml</code>配置</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">social:</span><br><span class="line">  GitHub: https://github.com/my0521 || fab fa-github</span><br><span class="line">  Gitee: https://gitee.com/my919 || fab fa-github</span><br><span class="line">  E-Mail: mailto:yeal166@163.com || fa fa-envelope</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="添加设计模式菜单"><a href="#添加设计模式菜单" class="headerlink" title="添加设计模式菜单"></a>添加设计模式菜单</h2><ol>
<li>添加目录<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo-starter&gt;hexo new page designmode</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Validating config</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Created: hexo-starter\source\designmode\index.md</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
<li><code>_config.next.yml</code>配置menu<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">designmode: /designmode/ || fa fa-paw</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
<li><code>zh-CN.yml</code> 的menu下新增<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">menu:</span><br><span class="line">  designmode: 设计模式</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
<li>更新<code>zh-CN.yml</code><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">copy  &quot;.\zh-CN.yml&quot; &quot;.\node_modules\hexo-theme-next\languages\zh-CN.yml&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
</ol>
]]></content>
      <tags>
        <tag>hexo</tag>
      </tags>
